snippet.title: Unobelisk Trailer
snippet.description:
English Unobelisk trailer. The game will release at some point of May 2020 on Itch.io.


The music played in the trailer is "Pursuit" by Scott Buckley – www.scottbuckley.com.au under the Creative Commons ‘Attribution 4.0 International’ (CC BY 4.0) License
